Class Panel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Panel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GUI
    public class Panel
extends java.lang.Object
implements GUI
    Represents a panel in a graphical user interface (GUI). A panel can contain other GUI elements and provide functionality.
